Lasting Judgment	CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.InquisitorJudgment				DESC:Your judgments do not end immediately.																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.7	BENEFIT:At the end of a combat in which you have used a judgment, your judgment continues to grant you its bonuses for 15 minutes. If a new combat starts within this time, your original judgment still ends 15 minutes after the last combat stopped. If you invoke a new judgment while your old judgment is active, your old judgment ends.
